## 7. Integration Points & Contracts

### 7.1 HTTP API Contract (locked at end of Task 1+4)

**`POST /api/chat`**
- Request: `Content-Type: application/json` ‚Äî `{ "prompt": string }`
- Response 200: `{ "response": string, "agentType": "weather" | "research" | "other" }`
- Response 400: `{ "error": string }` ‚Äî empty/missing prompt
- Response 500: `{ "error": string }` ‚Äî orchestrator/API failure

**`GET /`** ‚Üí `public/index.html` (served by `express.static`)

**`GET /*` (any static file)** ‚Üí served from `public/` if present, else 404

