**CSS approach ‚Äî dark modern chat:**
- Root color tokens: `--bg:#0d1117; --bg-elev:#161b22; --text:#e6edf3; --muted:#8b949e; --accent:#2f81f7; --user:#238636; --agent:#30363d;`
- `main#chat` is flex-column with `overflow-y:auto`, scrolls as messages append
- Message bubbles: `.msg.user` (right-aligned, accent bg) vs `.msg.agent` (left-aligned, panel bg)
- Composer is a sticky bottom bar with input + button
