| R2 | `path.join(__dirname, "..", "public")` breaks between ts-node and dist | Low | High | Verified resolution: ts-node ‚Üí `<proj>/src/../public`, dist ‚Üí `<proj>/dist/../public`, both = `<proj>/public`. Add a boot-time `fs.existsSync` check and log warning if missing. |
