## 3. Risk Assessment & Mitigation

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|-----------|
| **SDK ContentBlock type shape differs from assumption** (SDK is v0.90 ‚Äî recent) | Medium | Medium | After Task 2, run `tsc --noEmit` once; let the compiler surface mismatches. Cross-check against `node_modules/@anthropic-ai/sdk/resources/messages.d.ts` if needed. |
| **`claude-sonnet-4-5` model alias not available on the API key's account** | Low | High ‚Äî demo blocker | Verify with a one-shot `messages.create` before wiring the loop. Fallback: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929` or whatever the latest pinned Sonnet snapshot is. |
| **Infinite tool_use loop** (model keeps calling tools) | Low | Medium | Optional hard cap: `if (turn > 10) throw new Error(...)`. Not in spec but cheap insurance for demo. Document as a follow-up if omitted. |
| **`process.argv.slice(2).join(" ")` mangles quoted prompts with shell-special chars** | Low | Low | Document in README: *"Wrap prompts in quotes: `npm run dev -- \"your prompt\"`"*. Note the `--` is required for npm to pass args to the script. |
| **Missing `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`** in `.env` | Medium | Low (fails fast) | Already handled by `src/config/env.ts` with a clear error message ‚Äî no action needed. |
| **Stale `dist/` from a prior `tsc` run masks a broken build** | Low | Low | `npm run dev` uses `ts-node` directly (reads `src/`, not `dist/`), so this only bites `npm start`. Run `rm -rf dist && npm run build && npm start` as a final gate. |

